This is Guji Zone, Oromia. No internet for 100 km.

2
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:07,000
I open ELSIP. Works instantly – everything is saved on the phone.

3
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:14,000
Even without internet, I can complete a full inspection report.

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:18,000
Take evidence photos – saved locally.

5
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:22,000
Sign with finger.

6
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:28,000
Press “Generate Official Report” → PDF created in 3 seconds.

7
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:35,000
Full official report with photos, signatures, and QR code – created completely offline.

8
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:42,000
18 days later, I reach a town with internet…

9
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:48,000
…all 27 reports uploaded and verified in 8 seconds.

10
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:53,000
This is ELSIP — built for rural Ethiopia.

11
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:59,000
Live now at elsip.mols.gov.et – Thank you!
